{"tid":1433331,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"仲放唔低前度，可以點做","createTime":"2019-08-08T12:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:05:37.000Z","uid":121048,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec17463573a2617d2aecba616d429806ddb5364","tid":1433331,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"其實都分咗手差不多半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />分手之後以嚟都冇見過，但一直間唔中都會傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同佢好夾，女朋友嘅角色佢做得好好，但係最後因爲雙方屋企嘅原因而和平分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近排因為成日要發夢，所以分手嘅唔開心減淡咗好多，都冇時間傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啱今日知道佢會出現係我屋企附近，所以就想約佢見下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身都預咗佢唔會見我，但真係見到佢好直接拒絕我，話唔想見面嘅時候，個心真係好難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明當初幾忙都好，佢都唔會拒絕我，會盡量留翻啲時間見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />分手之後，我連見佢一面嘅資格都沒有了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我只係想上嚟叫下春發洩下，之後我會繼續專心發夢的</span>"},{"pid":"7dec61bf9b7383d1e3d1c4ca716912f12f9f8cf4","tid":1433331,"uid":80493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ec17463573a2617d2aecba616d429806ddb5364","tid":1433331,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"其實都分咗手差不多半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />分手之後以嚟都冇見過，但一直間唔中都會傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/